description: "Systematic debugging methodology for AFNM mods. Activate when errors occur or fixes aren't working."
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

See `docs/skills/systematic-debugging.md`.

Four phases: Root Cause Investigation → Pattern Analysis → Hypothesis Testing → Implementation.
- Stop after 3 failed fix attempts. Re-examine assumptions.
- Check SUPPLEMENTARY_GUIDE.md section 3 and 7 first.
- Use `bun run runtime:grep -- "<symbol>"` before guessing.
- Never fix without understanding why the fix works.
